snippet.title: Self-Defense Training Camp - Announcement Trailer (Xbox 360)
snippet.description:
Self-Defense Training Camp helps players develop the self-confidence they need to react more efficiently when facing troublesome situations, and it allows players to discover ways of protecting themselves from various forms of physical assault.

Read more here: http://www.gamespot.com/645626
